io.apptik.widget

Class MultiSlider.Thumb

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.apptik.widget.MultiSlider.Thumb
  • Enclosing class:
    MultiSlider

    public class MultiSlider.Thumb
extends java.lang.Object
    Thumb is the main object in MultiSlider. There could be 0, 1 or many thumbs. Each thumb has a min and max limit and a value which should always be between the limits. Each thumb defines a 'Range' the range is always between the value of the Thumb back to the previous Thumb's value or to the beginning of the track.
